name: Salus Floradix ijzer tabletten
ingredients:
gistextracten, rijstzetmeel, gedroogd extract (17,4 %): maltodextrine, spinazieblad (spinacia oleracea), brandnetelblad (urtica dioica), venkelvrucht (foeniculum vulgare), wortel (daucus carota), duizendguldenkruid (centaurium erythraea), anti-klontermiddel: siliciumdioxide, ijzergluconaat, rozenbottelextract (4 %) (rosa canina) (rozenbottelextract, maltodextrine), vitamine c, niacine,
 vulstof: celstof, anti-klontermiddel: siliciumdioxide / magnesiumstearaat / talc, coating: shellac, vitamine b6 (pyridoxine-chloride), vitamine b2 (riboflavine), vitamine b12 (cyanocobalamin), emulgator: polysorbate 80, vitamine b1 (thiamine chloridehydrochloride), foliumzuur, maltodextrine.
